[2;36m                    [0m         [39mtimeout.” This indicates that during a fuzzing session the process exceeded its [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mpredefined execution time limit and was halted.[0m                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Vulnerability type  [0m                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  No specific vulnerability type is mentioned in the issue. The message reflects a [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mstability or performance condition rather than a crash, memory corruption, or [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39msecurity flaw.[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Observations and findings  [0m                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  • The harness code served as the fuzzer’s entry point but did not itself trigger [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39ma crash or hang detectable by libFuzzer within the time budget.  [0m                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  • The timeout suggests that one or more code paths under test are executing for [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mtoo long or failing to return control promptly.  [0m                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  • There is no indication of a memory leak, assertion failure, or sanitizer [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mreport—only the fuzzer’s built-in time cutoff was reached.  [0m                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Areas for investigation  [0m                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  • Fuzzing harness implementation: review how inputs are fed into the code, and [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mconfirm that all expected exit conditions are reachable.  [0m                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  • Core logic under test: identify loops, recursive calls, or blocking operations [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mthat may lead to extended execution times.  [0m                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  • Performance hotspots: use profiling or instrumentation to find functions [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mconsuming excessive time per invocation.  [0m                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  • Fuzzer configuration: examine timeout settings, input generation parameters, [0m   [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m414[0m[39m:        if [0m[1;39m([0m[1;35mlist.size[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m > [0m[1;35mZipSecureFile.getMaxFileCount[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                    [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [1;35mZipSecureFile.getMaxFileCount[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m417[0m[39m:        [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m418[0m[39m:        final List<EntryTriple> entries =[0m                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m419[0m[39m:                [0m[1;35mlist.stream[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m                                                   [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m421[0m[39m:                        [0m[1;35m.map[0m[1;39m([0m[39mzae -> new [0m[1;35mEntryTriple[0m[1;39m([0m[39mzae, contentTypeManager[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m   [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m425[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode[0m[39m>[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<code>[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mpoi-ooxml/src/main/java/org/apache/poi/openxml4j/opc/internal/ZipHelper.jav[0m[1;92ma:174[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m19[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m7[0m                                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m174[0m[39m:    @[0m[1;35mSuppressWarnings[0m[1;39m([0m[32m"resource"[0m[1;39m)[0m                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m175[0m[39m:    public static ZipArchiveThresholdInputStream [0m[1;35mopenZipStream[0m[1;39m([0m[39mInputStream [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mstream[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m throws IOException [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m176[0m[39m:        return [0m[1;35mopenZipStream[0m[1;39m([0m[39mstream, true[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m177[0m[39m:    [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m178[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m179[0m[39m:    [0m[35m/[0m[39m**[0m                                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m180[0m[39m:     * Opens the specified stream as a secure zip. Closes the Input Stream.[0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m181[0m[39m:     *[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m182[0m[39m:     * @param stream The stream to open.[0m                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m183[0m[39m:     * @param closeStream whether to close the stream[0m                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m184[0m[39m:     * @return The zip stream freshly open.[0m                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m185[0m[39m:     *[0m[35m/[0m                                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m186[0m[39m:    @[0m[1;35mSuppressWarnings[0m[1;39m([0m[32m"resource"[0m[1;39m)[0m                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m187[0m[39m:    public static ZipArchiveThresholdInputStream [0m[1;35mopenZipStream[0m[1;39m([0m                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m188[0m[39m:            final InputStream stream, final boolean closeStream[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m throws [0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mIOException [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m189[0m[39m:        [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m Peek at the first few bytes to sanity check[0m                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m190[0m[39m:        InputStream checkedStream = [0m[1;35mFileMagic.prepareToCheckMagic[0m[1;39m([0m[39mstream[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m191[0m[39m:        [0m[1;35mverifyZipHeader[0m[1;39m([0m[39mcheckedStream[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m192[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m193[0m[39m:        final InputStream processStream = closeStream ? checkedStream : new [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;35mNoCloseInputStream[0m[1;39m([0m[39mcheckedStream[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m194[0m[39m:        [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m Open as a proper zip stream[0m                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m195[0m[39m:        return new [0m[1;35mZipArchiveThresholdInputStream[0m[1;39m([0m[39mnew [0m[1;35mZipArchiveInputStream[0m[1;39m([0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m196[0m[39m:                processStream, [0m[1;35mStandardCharsets.UTF_8.name[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, false, true[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m197[0m[39m:    [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode[0m[39m>[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode_snippets[0m[39m>[0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Fix Strategy[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<fix_strategy>[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[39m. Root Cause Analysis[0m                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - The libFuzzer “timeout” is caused by pathological inputs triggering very slow [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mstartup in the OOXML parsing code:[0m                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     a. ZipHelper.openZipStream eagerly wraps every InputStream in a [0m               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mZipArchiveThresholdInputStream backed by Commons-Compress’s ZipArchiveInputStream, [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mwhich in turn reads through the entire stream looking for local headers/central [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mdirectory before yielding any entries.[0m                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     b. [0m[1;35mZipPackage.getPartsImpl[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m then calls [0m                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;35mCollections.list[0m[1;39m([0m[1;35mzipArchive.getEntries[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m to exhaust the entire enumeration of [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mentries into a List, even when a reject-on-too-many-entries check exists; only [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mafter the full list is built does it check size > maxFileCount and abort.[0m           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     c. For malicious or fuzzed archives with many pseudo-entries [0m[1;39m([0m[39mor very large [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mstreams[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, [0m[1;39m([0m[39ma[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m and [0m[1;39m([0m[39mb[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m together can take far longer than libFuzzer’s time budget.[0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m. Strategy Overview[0m                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Stream the enumeration of ZipArchiveEntry objects in [0m[1;35mZipPackage.getPartsImpl[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39minstead of eagerly materializing the entire Enumeration. [0m                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Enforce the [0m[1;35mZipSecureFile.getMaxFileCount[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m limit during the first pass [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mthrough entries, so we abort immediately if the input contains too many entries.[0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Build the list of EntryTriple objects in a single loop [0m[1;39m([0m[39mfilter + map + [0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mnull-check[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m rather than via a stream pipeline over an intermediate list.[0m            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - After collecting all valid EntryTriple items [0m[1;39m([0m[39mor aborting early[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, sort that [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mlist and proceed with the existing logic unmodified.[0m                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - No changes to fuzz harness, no removal of functionality [0m[1;39m([0m[39mwe preserve the [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mmax-entry limit and full parsing for valid archives[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, no broad exception catching, [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mand all existing tests continue to pass for normal OOXML files.[0m                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3[0m[39m. Detailed Patch Steps[0m                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   A. In poi-ooxml/src/main/java/org/apache/poi/openxml4j/opc/ZipPackage.java:[0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     - Locate the [0m[1;35mgetPartsImpl[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m method around lines [0m[1;36m366[0m[39m–[0m[1;36m425[0m[39m.[0m                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     - Remove or comment out these lines:[0m                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         List<? extends ZipArchiveEntry> list = [0m[1;35mCollections.list[0m[1;39m([0m[39mzipEntries[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         if [0m[1;39m([0m[1;35mlist.size[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m > [0m[1;35mZipSecureFile.getMaxFileCount[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m[39m … [0m[1;39m}[0m                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         final List<EntryTriple> entries =[0m                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m             [0m[1;35mlist.stream[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m                 [0m[1;35m.filter[0m[1;39m([0m[39m…ignoreEntry…[0m[1;39m)[0m                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m                 [0m[1;35m.map[0m[1;39m([0m[39m…new EntryTriple…[0m[1;39m)[0m                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m                 [0m[1;35m.filter[0m[1;39m([0m[39m…partName!=null…[0m[1;39m)[0m                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m                 [0m[1;35m.sorted[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m                 [0m[1;35m.collect[0m[1;39m([0m[1;35mCollectors.toList[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     - Replace them with a single-pass loop:[0m                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         long maxCount = [0m[1;35mZipSecureFile.getMaxFileCount[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         List<EntryTriple> entries = new ArrayList<>[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         long count = [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m;[0m                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         while [0m[1;39m([0m[1;35mzipEntries.hasMoreElements[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m             ZipArchiveEntry zae = [0m[1;35mzipEntries.nextElement[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m             if [0m[1;39m([0m[39m++count > maxCount[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m                 throw new [0m[1;35mInvalidFormatException[0m[1;39m([0m                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m                     [0m[1;35mString.format[0m[1;39m([0m[39mLocale.ROOT,[0m                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m                                   ZipSecureFile.MAX_FILE_COUNT_MSG,[0m                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m                                   maxCount[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m             [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m             if [0m[1;39m([0m[39m![0m[1;35mignoreEntry[0m[1;39m([0m[39mzae[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m                 EntryTriple et = new [0m[1;35mEntryTriple[0m[1;39m([0m[39mzae, contentTypeManager[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m                 if [0m[1;39m([0m[39met.partName != null[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m                     [0m[1;35mentries.add[0m[1;39m([0m[39met[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m                 [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m             [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m existing sort[0m                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         [0m[1;35mCollections.sort[0m[1;39m([0m[39mentries[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     - Keep all subsequent logic [0m[1;39m([0m[39miterating through entries list, building [0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mrelationships[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m unchanged.[0m                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   B. Rationale[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     - We preserve exactly the same semantic behavior:[0m                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       • The identical max-file-count limit is enforced.[0m                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       • The final list of parts [0m[1;39m([0m[39mEntryTriple[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m and the sort order are unchanged.[0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       • Any archive with ≤ maxCount entries is fully processed.[0m                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     - We eliminate:[0m                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       • The intermediate “Collections.list” that fully exhausts the enumeration [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39meven on huge inputs.[0m                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       • The multi-stage stream pipeline with its multiple passes.[0m                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     - We short-circuit large inputs immediately as soon as the limit is exceeded, [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mdramatically reducing worst-case runtime.[0m                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     - For normal Excel files [0m[1;39m([0m[39mtens to low hundreds of entries[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, the behavior and [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mperformance are virtually identical.[0m                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m4[0m[39m. Impact and Side-Effects[0m                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Positive: fuzz targets now see an early InvalidFormatException for archives [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mthat exceed the configured max entry count, preventing long enumeration or sorting [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mdelays and avoiding libFuzzer timeouts.[0m                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - No change in public API or behavior for well-formed OOXML files.[0m               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Existing unit and integration tests [0m[1;39m([0m[39mwhich use normal spreadsheets[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m remain [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39munaffected.[0m                                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Security: we retain and strengthen the anti-zip-bomb guard by enforcing it as [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39msoon as possible.[0m                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m5[0m[39m. Verification[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Add regression tests feeding an archive with [0m[1;39m([0m[39mmaxCount + [0m[1;36m1[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m empty entries via [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;35mOPCPackage.open[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m: expect InvalidFormatException in under a few milliseconds.[0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Run existing POI test suite for XSSF to confirm nothing else is broken.[0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Rerun libFuzzer harness against the patched code to verify that the timeout no[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mlonger occurs on pathological inputs [0m[1;39m([0m[39mthey now abort early[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.[0m                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m6[0m[39m. Optional Further Optimizations [0m[1;39m([0m[39mdeferred[0m[1;39m)[0m                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - In a later patch, consider adding similar streaming + early-break [0m             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39moptimizations for other enumeration-based methods in OPCPackage subclasses.[0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Optionally provide a system property to tune maxCount at runtime [0m[1;39m([0m[39me.g., for [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mvery large corporate spreadsheets[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m without code changes.[0m                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mfix_strategy[0m[1m>[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         ===Evaluation [33mEnd[0m===                                                                [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [39m-                        [0m[1;35m.filter[0m[1;39m([0m[39mzipArchiveEntry -> ![0m[1;35mignoreEntry[0m[1;39m([0m[39mzipArchiveEntry[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m-                        [0m[1;35m.map[0m[1;39m([0m[39mzae -> new [0m[1;35mEntryTriple[0m[1;39m([0m[39mzae, contentTypeManager[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m-                        [0m[1;35m.filter[0m[1;39m([0m[39mmm -> mm.partName != null[0m[1;39m)[0m                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m-                        [0m[1;35m.sorted[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m-                        [0m[1;35m.collect[0m[1;39m([0m[1;35mCollectors.toList[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m+        long maxCount = [0m[1;35mZipSecureFile.getMaxFileCount[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m+        java.util.List<EntryTriple> entries = new java.util.ArrayList<>[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m+        long count = [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m;[0m                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m+        while [0m[1;39m([0m[1;35mzipEntries.hasMoreElements[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m+            ZipArchiveEntry zae = [0m[1;35mzipEntries.nextElement[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m+            if [0m[1;39m([0m[39m++count > maxCount[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m+                throw new [0m[1;35mInvalidFormatException[0m[1;39m([0m[1;35mString.format[0m[1;39m([0m                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m+                        Locale.ROOT, ZipSecureFile.MAX_FILE_COUNT_MSG, maxCount[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m+            [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m+            if [0m[1;39m([0m[39m![0m[1;35mignoreEntry[0m[1;39m([0m[39mzae[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m+                EntryTriple et = new [0m[1;35mEntryTriple[0m[1;39m([0m[39mzae, contentTypeManager[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m+                if [0m[1;39m([0m[39met.partName != null[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m+                    [0m[1;35mentries.add[0m[1;39m([0m[39met[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m+                [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m+            [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m+        [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m+        [0m[1;35mCollections.sort[0m[1;39m([0m[39mentries[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m [0m                                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         for [0m[1;39m([0m[39mfinal EntryTriple et : entries[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m             [0m[1;35met.register[0m[1;39m([0m[39mnewPartList[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m===Patch [0m[33mResult[0m[39m===[0m                                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mERROR: libFuzzer: timeout[0m                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m===[0m[33mIssue[0m[39m===[0m                                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mERROR: libFuzzer: timeout[0m                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m===Evaluation [0m[33mReport[0m[39m===[0m                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m# Evaluation Report[0m                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Summary[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mThe project’s fuzzing harness reported a persistent timeout when running against [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mthe OPC/ZIP handling code. To address this, a patch rewrote the logic in [0m           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`ZipPackage.java` for enumerating and filtering ZIP entries, replacing a two-pass, [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mstream-based approach with a single-pass loop that enforces the maximum‐file‐count [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcheck early and then collects, filters, and sorts entries. After applying the [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mpatch, the fuzzer still reports the same `ERROR: libFuzzer: timeout`, indicating no[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mchange in the timeout behavior.[0m                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Description[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[39m. Initial Issue  [0m                                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - The fuzzing infrastructure [0m[1;39m([0m[39mlibFuzzer[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m consistently times out when exercising [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mthe code that reads and processes ZIP packages [0m[1;39m([0m[39mOPC containers[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.  [0m                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - No stack traces or exception messages are produced beyond `ERROR: libFuzzer: [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mtimeout`, so the failure manifests solely as a stalled or extremely slow execution.[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m. Key Observations  [0m                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - The timeout indicates possible performance bottlenecks or unbounded loops [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mrather than a direct crash or exception.  [0m                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - The problematic code is in `org.apache.poi.openxml4j.opc.ZipPackage`, around [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mthe collection and filtering of ZIP entries.  [0m                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Original implementation:  [0m                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     • Converts the entire `zipEntries` enumeration into a `List`  [0m                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     • Enforces the maximum file count check after list creation  [0m                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     • Uses Java streams [0m[1;39m([0m[39m`filter`, `map`, `sorted`, `collect`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m to build the final [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mlist  [0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3[0m[39m. Patch Attempt  [0m                                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Location: [0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`poi-ooxml/src/main/java/org/apache/poi/openxml4j/opc/ZipPackage.java`  [0m            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Changes made:  [0m                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     • Introduced `long maxCount = [0m[1;35mZipSecureFile.getMaxFileCount[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` and an explicit[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcounter `count`.  [0m                                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     • Replaced `[0m[1;35mCollections.list[0m[1;39m([0m[39mzipEntries[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` + stream operations with a `while [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m([0m[1;35mzipEntries.hasMoreElements[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` loop.  [0m                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     • Increment `count` on each iteration; throw `InvalidFormatException` as soon [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mas `count` exceeds `maxCount`.  [0m                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     • Within the same loop, apply `[0m[1;35mignoreEntry[0m[1;39m([0m[39mzae[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` and build an [0m                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`ArrayList<EntryTriple>` only for entries whose `partName` is non-null.  [0m           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     • After the loop, call `[0m[1;35mCollections.sort[0m[1;39m([0m[39mentries[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` instead of using the [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mstream’s `[0m[1;35msorted[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` step.  [0m                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     • All other downstream logic [0m[1;39m([0m[39mregistering entries[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m is unchanged.  [0m             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Patch result: The fuzzer run still ends in `ERROR: libFuzzer: timeout`, [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mindicating that performance or hanging behavior remains unaddressed.[0m                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m4[0m[39m. Areas for Further Investigation  [0m                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - The ZIP enumeration/loading strategy in `ZipPackage`—particularly if [0m          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`[0m[1;35mhasMoreElements[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` or `[0m[1;35mnextElement[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` may block or re-scan entries.  [0m              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - The behavior of `EntryTriple` construction and `contentTypeManager` [0m           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39minteractions; potential expensive I/O or repeated metadata lookups.  [0m               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - The sorting step [0m[1;39m([0m[39m`[0m[1;35mCollections.sort[0m[1;39m([0m[39mentries[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m once the list is built—ensure [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mno pathological data sizes or comparator issues.  [0m                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Any recursive or post-processing paths invoked by `[0m[1;35met.register[0m[1;39m([0m[39mnewPartList[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mthat might traverse large object graphs.  [0m                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Configuration of `ZipSecureFile` limits and whether fuzzer inputs can bypass [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mor stress those boundaries, leading to excessive processing.  [0m                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Interaction between the fuzzing harness and the OPC/ZIP code—confirm that the [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mharness does not inadvertently feed extremely large archives or stall on I/O.[0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Initial Issue Log[0m                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mHere is the initial issue log of the codebase:[0m                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<issue>[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mERROR: libFuzzer: timeout[0m                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95missue[0m[39m>[0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Additional Issue Log[0m                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mHere is the additional issue log after the last patch attempt:[0m                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<additional_issue>[0m                                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mERROR: libFuzzer: timeout[0m                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95madditional_issue[0m[39m>[0m                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Notes[0m                                                                            [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m33[0m[39m: * Provides a way to get at all the ZipEntries[0m                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m34[0m[39m: *  from a ZipInputStream, as many times as required.[0m                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m35[0m[39m: * Allows a ZipInputStream to be treated much like[0m                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m36[0m[39m: *  a ZipFile, for a price in terms of memory.[0m                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m37[0m[39m: * Be sure to call [0m[1;39m{[0m[39m@link #[0m[1;35mclose[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m}[0m[39m as soon as you're[0m                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m38[0m[39m: *  done, to free up that memory![0m                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m39[0m[39m: *[0m[35m/[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m40[0m[39m:public class ZipInputStreamZipEntrySource implements ZipEntrySource [0m[1;39m{[0m            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m41[0m[39m:    private static int thresholdForTempFiles = [0m[1;36m-1[0m[39m;[0m                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m42[0m[39m:    private static boolean encryptTempFiles = false;[0m                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m43[0m[39m:    private final Map<String, ZipArchiveFakeEntry> zipEntries = new HashMap<>[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m44[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m45[0m[39m:    private InputStream streamToClose;[0m                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m46[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m47[0m[39m:    [0m[35m/[0m[39m**[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m48[0m[39m:     * Set the threshold at which a zip entry is regarded as too large for [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mholding in memory[0m                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m49[0m[39m:     * and the data is put in a temp file instead[0m                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m50[0m[39m:     * @param thresholdBytes number of bytes at which a zip entry is regarded as[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mtoo large for holding in memory[0m                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m51[0m[39m:     *                       and the data is put in a temp file instead - [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mdefaults to [0m[1;36m-1[0m[39m meaning temp files are not used[0m                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m52[0m[39m:     *                       and that zip entries with more than 2GB of data [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mafter decompressing will fail, [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m means all[0m                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m53[0m[39m:     *                       zip entries are stored in temp files. A threshold [0m  [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m182[0m[39m:     * security vulnerabilities when documents are provided by users.[0m           [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m184[0m[39m:     * @param maxTextSize the max. file size of a single zip entry[0m              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m185[0m[39m:     * @throws IllegalArgumentException for negative maxTextSize[0m                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m186[0m[39m:     *[0m[35m/[0m                                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m187[0m[39m:    public static void [0m[1;35msetMaxTextSize[0m[1;39m([0m[39mlong maxTextSize[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m188[0m[39m:        if [0m[1;39m([0m[39mmaxTextSize < [0m[1;36m0[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                  [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m198[0m[39m:     *[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m199[0m[39m:     * @return The max accepted text size.[0m                                      [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m92[0m[39m:            data = [0m[1;39m([0m[39mentrySize == [0m[1;36m-1[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m ? [0m[1;35mIOUtils.toByteArrayWithMaxLength[0m[1;39m([0m[39minp, [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;35mgetMaxEntrySize[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m :[0m                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m93[0m[39m:                    [0m[1;35mIOUtils.toByteArray[0m[1;39m([0m[39minp, entrySize, [0m[1;35mgetMaxEntrySize[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m94[0m[39m:        [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode[0m[39m>[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<code>[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mpoi-ooxml/src/main/java/org/apache/poi/openxml4j/util/ZipFileZipEntrySource.jav[0m[1;92ma:52[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m-[0m[1;36m57[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m52[0m[39m:    public Enumeration<? extends ZipArchiveEntry> [0m[1;35mgetEntries[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m53[0m[39m:        if [0m[1;39m([0m[39mzipArchive == null[0m[1;39m)[0m                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m54[0m[39m:            throw new [0m[1;35mIllegalStateException[0m[1;39m([0m[32m"Zip File is closed"[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m55[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m56[0m[39m:        return [0m[1;35mzipArchive.getEntries[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m57[0m[39m:    [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode[0m[39m>[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode_snippets[0m[39m>[0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Fix Strategy[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<fix_strategy>[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[39m. Root Cause Analysis[0m                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - The timeout is caused primarily by the eager, full decompression of all ZIP [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mentries in the stream‐based source [0m[1;39m([0m[39m`ZipInputStreamZipEntrySource`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, which on [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mconstruction reads every entry’s data via `ZipArchiveFakeEntry` [0m[1;39m([0m[39mcopying or [0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mbuffering entire contents[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, before any part‐filtering occurs.  [0m                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - The last patch only optimized the one‐pass enumeration in `[0m[1;35mgetPartsImpl[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`, [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mbut did not address the upstream cost of streaming and decompressing every entry on[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`[0m[1;35mZipPackage[0m[1;39m([0m[39mInputStream…[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` construction.  [0m                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - By contrast, the file‐based source [0m[1;39m([0m[39m`ZipFileZipEntrySource` wrapping Apache [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mCommons Compress’s `ZipFile`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m only reads the central directory [0m[1;39m([0m[39mmetadata[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m lazily [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mand defers entry decompression to `[0m[1;35mgetInputStream[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`, which is far more efficient [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mfor enumeration and filtering.  [0m                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m. Strategy Overview[0m                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - For **stream‐based** constructors [0m[1;39m([0m[39m`[0m[1;35mZipPackage[0m[1;39m([0m[39mInputStream,…[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, bypass [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`ZipInputStreamZipEntrySource` entirely. Instead, materialize the incoming [0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`InputStream` into a temporary on‐disk ZIP file and then open it via the efficient [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`ZipFileZipEntrySource` path.  [0m                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Preserve the existing `[0m[1;35mgetPartsImpl[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` single‐pass enumeration and filtering [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mlogic [0m[1;39m([0m[39mthe last patch[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m to enforce `maxFileCount`, `[0m[1;35mignoreEntry[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`, part‐name [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mfiltering, and sorting.  [0m                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Schedule deletion of the temporary file on JVM exit [0m[1;39m([0m[39mor when closing the [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mpackage[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m to avoid resource leaks.  [0m                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - This approach:[0m                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     • Eliminates the eager full decompression in `ZipInputStreamZipEntrySource`.  [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     • Retains all security checks [0m[1;39m([0m[39mvia `ZipSecureFile` limits[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m and existing [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mpart‐registration logic.  [0m                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     • Requires no modifications to the fuzz harness, tests, or external libraries.[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3[0m[39m. Implementation Steps[0m                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   A. Reapply and keep the one‐pass enumeration patch in `[0m[1;35mgetPartsImpl[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`[0m           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      - Ensure the loop over `[0m[1;35mzipArchive.getEntries[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` enforces `maxFileCount`, [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcalls `[0m[1;35mignoreEntry[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`, constructs `EntryTriple`, filters null `partName`, and [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mfinally sorts, exactly as in the last patch.  [0m                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      - This preserves the improvements in filtering and sorting locality.  [0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   [0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   B. Modify the `InputStream` constructor in `ZipPackage` [0m[1;39m([0m[39maround lines [0m[1;36m208[0m[39m–[0m[1;36m213[0m[1;39m)[0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      - Replace:[0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         ```[0m                                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         try [0m[1;39m([0m[39mZipArchiveThresholdInputStream zis = [0m[1;35mZipHelper.openZipStream[0m[1;39m([0m[39min, [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcloseStream[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m             this.zipArchive = new [0m[1;35mZipInputStreamZipEntrySource[0m[1;39m([0m[39mzis[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         ```[0m                                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      - With logic to:[0m                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         [0m[1;36m1[0m[39m. Create a `File tmp = [0m[1;35mTempFile.createTempFile[0m[1;39m([0m[32m"poi-zip-package"[0m[39m, [0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [32m".zip"[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`.[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         [0m[1;36m2[0m[39m. Copy the entire `in` stream into `tmp` using `[0m[1;35mIOUtils.copy[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`.[0m          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         [0m[1;36m3[0m[39m. If `closeStream` is `true`, close the original `in`.[0m                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         [0m[1;36m4[0m[39m. Open `tmp` via `[0m[1;35mZipHelper.openZipFile[0m[1;39m([0m[39mtmp[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` to get a `ZipFile` [0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m([0m[39mactually a `ZipSecureFile` as appropriate[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.  [0m                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         [0m[1;36m5[0m[39m. Wrap it in `new [0m[1;35mZipFileZipEntrySource[0m[1;39m([0m[39mzipFile[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`.[0m                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         [0m[1;36m6[0m[39m. Call `[0m[1;35mtmp.deleteOnExit[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` to cleanup.  [0m                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      - This change routes stream‐based input through the file‐based, [0m              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcentral‐directory approach, deferring any decompression until `[0m[1;35mgetInputStream[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcalls, and avoiding upfront memory/temp‐file creation for every entry.[0m              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   C. Handle temporary‐file cleanup[0m                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      - As a minimal approach, invoke `[0m[1;35mtmp.deleteOnExit[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`.  [0m                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      - Optionally, extend `[0m[1;35mZipFileZipEntrySource.close[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` or `[0m[1;35mZipPackage.close[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mto explicitly delete the file when the package is closed, ensuring no leftover [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mfiles.[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m4[0m[39m. Justification[0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Writing to a temp file and using `ZipFileZipEntrySource`:[0m                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     • Reads only metadata at enumeration time [0m[1;39m([0m[39mcentral directory[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m rather than full[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mdecompression, drastically reducing initial I/O and CPU cost.  [0m                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     • Enforces `ZipSecureFile` limits uniformly, including `maxFileCount`, on the [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mfile‐based path.  [0m                                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     • Keeps the existing `[0m[1;35mgetPartsImpl[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` logic intact, so no behavior change in [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mpart creation/registration.  [0m                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     • Maintains fuzzer harness compatibility—input is still consumed via the same [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`[0m[1;35mZipPackage[0m[1;39m([0m[39mInputStream…[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` API, only under the covers it goes through a temp file.[0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - The additional I/O cost of copying the compressed stream to disk is linear in [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcompressed size and typically lower overhead than decompressing every entry in [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mfull. Even for adversarial inputs, this will significantly reduce face‐time in the [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mexpensive `ZipInputStreamZipEntrySource` constructor.[0m                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m5[0m[39m. Potential Side Effects & Mitigation[0m                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Temporary files: mitigated by `[0m[1;35mdeleteOnExit[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` and/or explicit deletion on [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mpackage close.  [0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Slight delay in constructor due to compressed‐stream copy: acceptable tradeoff[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mfor avoiding full decompression of all entries.  [0m                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Memory usage: now limited by the compressed‐stream buffer instead of potential[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mmulti‐GB decompressed data.  [0m                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - No changes to tests or harness; existing functionality is preserved.[0m           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m6[0m[39m. References & Consistency[0m                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Mirrors the file‐based path in the `File` constructor of `ZipPackage`, which [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39malready falls back to `ZipFileZipEntrySource`.  [0m                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Reuses existing `[0m[1;35mZipHelper.openZipFile[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` and `ZipFileZipEntrySource` classes [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mwithout external library changes.  [0m                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**No harness code or external library patches are required.** This unified [0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mfile‐based enumeration approach resolves the timeout by eliminating the eager [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mdecompression bottleneck.  [0m                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mfix_strategy[0m[1m>[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         ===Evaluation [33mEnd[0m===                                                                [2m                [0m
