[2;36m                    [0m         [39m===Evaluation [0m[33mReport[0m[39m===[0m                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m# Evaluation Report[0m                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Summary[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mThe codebase was exhibiting a persistent libFuzzer timeout [0m[1;39m([0m[39m“ERROR: libFuzzer: [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mtimeout”[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m when exercising the OPC/ZIP handling paths. An attempted patch rerouted [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mstream-based ZIP input through a temporary file [0m[1;39m([0m[39musing `TempFile.createTempFile` [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mand `ZipHelper.openZipFile`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m and replaced a stream-to-list + sort pipeline with an [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mexplicit loop counting entries and sorting afterwards. After applying this patch, [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mthe fuzzer still timed out with the same error, indicating that the changes did not[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mresolve the performance or hang issue.[0m                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Description[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[39m. Initial issue  [0m                                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - While fuzzing the Apache POI OOXML ZIP handling [0m                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m([0m[39m`poi-ooxml/src/main/java/org/apache/poi/openxml4j/opc/ZipPackage.java`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, libFuzzer[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mreported a timeout.  [0m                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - The error log simply shows `ERROR: libFuzzer: timeout`, with no stack trace or[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mexception details.  [0m                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - The harness code [0m[1;39m([0m[39mthe entry point used by the fuzzer[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m is not believed to be [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mthe root cause; it only drives the library under test.[0m                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m. Observations from the initial issue  [0m                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - The timeout suggests either an infinite loop, excessive blocking I/O, or very [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mlong processing of certain inputs.  [0m                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - No Java exceptions or error messages were emitted beyond the fuzzer timeout [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mitself.  [0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - The problematic code regions under fuzz involve:  [0m                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     • Construction of `ZipPackage` from a generic `InputStream`.  [0m                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     • Iteration and filtering of ZIP entries, with a security check on maximum [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mfile count.  [0m                                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3[0m[39m. Patch attempt  [0m                                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - In the `[0m[1;35mZipPackage[0m[1;39m([0m[39mInputStream, [0m[33m...[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` constructor [0m[1;39m([0m[39maround line [0m[1;36m207[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m:  [0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     • Original: wrapped the input stream in a `ZipArchiveThresholdInputStream` and[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mpassed it directly to a streaming ZIP entry source.  [0m                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     • Patched:  [0m                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       – Copy the entire `InputStream` to a temp file via `TempFile.createTempFile`[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m+ `Files.newOutputStream`.  [0m                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       – Close the original stream if `closeStream` is true.  [0m                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       – Open the temp file as an [0m                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`org.apache.commons.compress.archivers.zip.ZipFile` and use [0m                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`ZipFileZipEntrySource`.  [0m                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       – Mark the temp file for deletion on exit.  [0m                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - In the relationships/parts loading section [0m[1;39m([0m[39maround line [0m[1;36m410[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m:  [0m                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     • Original: collected all entries into a `List`, threw if count exceeds [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`[0m[1;35mZipSecureFile.getMaxFileCount[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`, then streamed through filtering, mapping, [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39msorting, and collecting.  [0m                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     • Patched:  [0m                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       – Iterate `zipEntries` with a `while [0m[1;39m([0m[1;35mhasMoreElements[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` loop.  [0m            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       – Maintain a counter and throw early if the max file count is exceeded.  [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       – Add non-ignored entries to a modifiable `ArrayList<EntryTriple>`.  [0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       – After iteration, invoke `[0m[1;35mCollections.sort[0m[1;39m([0m[39mentries[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` on the accumulated [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mlist.  [0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m4[0m[39m. Patch result  [0m                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Upon rebuilding and rerunning the fuzz target, the same `ERROR: libFuzzer: [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mtimeout` was observed.  [0m                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - No new log output or exception stack traces resulted from the patch.  [0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m5[0m[39m. Code areas for further investigation  [0m                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - The `ZipPackage` constructor logic, in particular:  [0m                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     • Performance and resource behavior of `TempFile.createTempFile` + file copy [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mfor large streams.  [0m                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     • Differences between streaming [0m[1;39m([0m[39m`ZipInputStreamZipEntrySource`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m and [0m          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mrandom-access [0m[1;39m([0m[39m`ZipFileZipEntrySource`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m ZIP processing.  [0m                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - The ZIP entry iteration path:  [0m                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     • Potential blocking or infinite loop conditions in [0m                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`[0m[1;35mzipEntries.hasMoreElements[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` or `[0m[1;35mzipEntries.nextElement[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`.  [0m                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     • The impact of the entry-count check and sorting on performance for large or [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mmaliciously crafted ZIPs.  [0m                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Any interaction with `OPCComplianceFlags` or additional validation hooks in [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`ZipPackage`.  [0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Underlying I/O or synchronization points in `org.apache.commons.compress` and [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`ZipHelper` utilities that may cause hangs under certain input patterns.[0m            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Initial Issue Log[0m                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mHere is the initial issue log of the codebase:[0m                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<issue>[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mERROR: libFuzzer: timeout[0m                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95missue[0m[39m>[0m                                                                            [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Fix Strategy[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<fix_strategy>[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[39m. Fast‐fail raw non-ZIP inputs before any heavy work  [0m                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - In the `[0m[1;35mZipPackage[0m[1;39m([0m[39mInputStream in, [0m[33m...[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` constructor, immediately wrap the [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mincoming stream in a small `BufferedInputStream`, `[0m[1;35mmark[0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m4[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`, and read the first [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mfour bytes. Check for the ZIP magic [0m[1;39m([0m[39m“PK\[0m[1;36m003[0m[39m\[0m[1;36m004[0m[39m” or other valid local‐file‐header [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39msignatures[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.  [0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - If the magic does not match, reset or close the stream [0m[1;39m([0m[39mdepending on [0m          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`closeStream`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, and throw a `NotOfficeXmlFileException` [0m[1;39m([0m[39mor a consistent [0m           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`InvalidFormatException`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.  [0m                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Rationale: most fuzzer inputs are random bytes. Catching non-ZIP data in <[0m[1;36m1[0m[39m ms[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mand failing avoids the expensive temp-file copy or any decompression on totally [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mirrelevant inputs.[0m                                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m. Eliminate the slow fallback to streaming decompression on file-based [0m            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mconstruction  [0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - In the `[0m[1;35mZipPackage[0m[1;39m([0m[39mFile file, [0m[33m...[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` constructor, replace the catch blocks for [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`InvalidZipException` and generic `IOException` so that instead of logging a [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mwarning and calling `[0m[1;35mopenZipEntrySourceStream[0m[1;39m([0m[39mfile[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`, the code rethrows an [0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`InvalidFormatException` or wraps into an `InvalidOperationException`.  [0m            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Rationale: the current fallback re-invokes the streaming path, which [0m          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39munconditionally decompresses every entry [0m[1;39m([0m[39mand for malformed archives, scans to [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mEOF[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, leading to hangs or timeouts. By failing fast on a central‐directory parse [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39merror, we remove the pathological streaming branch entirely while preserving the [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mvalid random-access path.[0m                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3[0m[39m. Convert eager entry decompression into lazy metadata parsing  [0m                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Refactor `ZipInputStreamZipEntrySource` so that its constructor does NOT call [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`[0m[1;35mgetNextEntry[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` and immediately build a full `ZipArchiveFakeEntry` [0m[1;39m([0m[39mwhich [0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mdecompresses content[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m for each entry. Instead:  [0m                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     a. Loop over the `ZipArchiveInputStream` to read only the header metadata [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m([0m[39mentry name, size, comment[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m and then call `[0m[1;35mcloseEntry[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` [0m[1;39m([0m[39mor skip the entry data[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mto move to the next header.  [0m                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     b. Store a lightweight metadata descriptor [0m[1;39m([0m[39mfile name, central‐directory [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mfields, compressed size, etc.[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m in the internal `zipEntries` map.  [0m                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     c. Defer any data decompression to the moment the consumer actually calls [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`[0m[1;35mgetInputStream[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` for a particular entry.  [0m                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Rationale: this change ensures that constructing the entry source only costs [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;35mO[0m[1;39m([0m[39mn × header-scan[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m without decompressing or buffering every entry body. It [0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mdramatically reduces I/O and CPU on large or maliciously crafted archives.[0m          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m4[0m[39m. Introduce a raw-bytes threshold on stream-to-temp-file copy  [0m                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - When copying `in` → `tmp` via `IOUtils.copy`, wrap `in` in a [0m                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`BoundedInputStream` [0m[1;39m([0m[39mor reuse `ZipArchiveThresholdInputStream` in a pass‐through [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mmode[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m so that if the total raw bytes exceed a defined ceiling [0m[1;39m([0m[39mfor example, [0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`[0m[1;35mZipSecureFile.getMaxEntrySize[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` or a new `POIFS.MAX_ZIP_SIZE`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, the code aborts [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mwith a clear `IOException`.  [0m                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Rationale: this caps disk I/O and memory usage on overly large inputs, [0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mpreserving service availability under fuzz and malicious use.[0m                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m5[0m[39m. Preservation of existing functionality and thresholds  [0m                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Valid ZIP files with a correct central directory still hit the [0m                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`ZipHelper.openZipFile` → `ZipFileZipEntrySource` path, unchanged in logic or [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mperformance characteristics.  [0m                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - The file-count, size, and decompression‐ratio checks remain intact via [0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`ZipSecureFile` and `ZipArchiveThresholdInputStream` where applicable.  [0m            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - No harness, fuzzing flags, or external library code is modified—only core [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mOPC/ZIP handling in `ZipPackage` and `ZipInputStreamZipEntrySource` is touched.[0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m6[0m[39m. Testing and verification  [0m                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Add unit tests feeding random non-ZIP byte arrays to the `InputStream` [0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mconstructor—assert an immediate `NotOfficeXmlFileException` without temp-file [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcreation.  [0m                                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Verify that valid small OOXML packages still open successfully and that parts [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39menumeration, filtering, sorting, and all OPC compliance flags operate as before.  [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Performance smoke tests: inject large [0m[1;39m([0m[39m>[0m[1;36m100[0m[39m MB[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m inputs and confirm sub-second [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mfast-fail on magic check or threshold breach rather than a libFuzzer timeout.[0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mBy combining an early magic-header gate, strict thresholds on raw data copy, and [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mlazy entry metadata parsing [0m[1;39m([0m[39mplus removing the slow streaming fallback[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, this [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mstrategy directly addresses the root cause of the hanging/decompression loops [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mwithout sacrificing existing ZIP/OPC compliance or breaking downstream [0m             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mfunctionality.  [0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mfix_strategy[0m[1m>[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         ===Evaluation [33mEnd[0m===                                                                [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [39m===Patch [0m[33mResult[0m[39m===[0m                                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mERROR: libFuzzer: timeout[0m                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m===[0m[33mIssue[0m[39m===[0m                                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mERROR: libFuzzer: timeout[0m                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m===Evaluation [0m[33mReport[0m[39m===[0m                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m# Evaluation Report[0m                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Summary[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mThe initial issue reported by the fuzzing harness was a libFuzzer timeout when [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mexercising the Apache POI codebase. In response, a patch was introduced in [0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mZipPackage.java to pre-validate ZIP inputs by checking the PK magic header, then [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcopy the input into a bounded temporary file before opening it as a ZIP to enforce [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39msize limits. After applying that patch, the build failed in poi-ooxml due to:[0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- A missing `[0m[1;35mgetByteCount[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` method on the Commons-IO `BoundedInputStream` class.[0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- An illegal multi-catch combining a subclass [0m[1;39m([0m[39m`InvalidZipException`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m with its [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39msupertype [0m[1;39m([0m[39m`IOException`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.[0m                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Two additional compilation errors in BaseXSSFEvaluationWorkbook.java [0m[1;39m([0m[39munrelated [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mto the patch[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m causing the overall build to fail.[0m                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Description[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[39m. Initial Issue  [0m                                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - The only visible symptom was:  [0m                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     `ERROR: libFuzzer: timeout`  [0m                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - No stack trace or exception details were provided by the harness.  [0m            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m. Patch Attempt  [0m                                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Location: [0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`poi-ooxml/src/main/java/org/apache/poi/openxml4j/opc/ZipPackage.java`  [0m            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Added logic to buffer the incoming `InputStream`, read and verify the first [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mfour bytes against ZIP signatures [0m[1;39m([0m[39m`PK\[0m[1;36m003[0m[39m\[0m[1;36m004[0m[39m`, etc.[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, and reject non-ZIP inputs [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mwith a `NotOfficeXmlFileException`.  [0m                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Copied the validated stream into a bounded temporary file [0m[1;39m([0m[39mlimit = [0m            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mmaxEntrySize × maxFileCount from `ZipSecureFile`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, then opened it via [0m              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`[0m[1;35mZipHelper.openZipFile[0m[1;39m([0m[39mtmp[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`.  [0m                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Switched from `ZipInputStreamZipEntrySource` to `ZipFileZipEntrySource`.  [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Modified another constructor to merge `InvalidZipException` and `IOException` [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39minto a single catch.[0m                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3[0m[39m. Build Log After Patch  [0m                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Hundreds of warnings across modules [0m[1;39m([0m[39munchecked casts, deprecations[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.  [0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Errors in `poi-ooxml:compileJava`:  [0m                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     * In ZipPackage.java:  [0m                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       - `cannot find symbol: method [0m[1;35mgetByteCount[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` on [0m                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`org.apache.commons.io.input.BoundedInputStream`  [0m                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       - “Alternatives in a multi-catch statement cannot be related by subclassing”[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mfor `catch [0m[1;39m([0m[39mInvalidZipException | IOException e[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`  [0m                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     * In BaseXSSFEvaluationWorkbook.java: two compilation errors [0m[1;39m([0m[39mdeprecated API [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39muse, but treated as errors under current flags[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.  [0m                                  [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m11[0m[39m:   Unless required by applicable law or agreed to in writing, software[0m           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m12[0m[39m:   distributed under the License is distributed on an [0m[32m"AS IS"[0m[39m BASIS,[0m             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m13[0m[39m:   WITHOUT WARRANTIES OR CONDITIONS OF ANY KIND, either express or implied.[0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m14[0m[39m:   See the License for the specific language governing permissions and[0m           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m15[0m[39m:   limitations under the License.[0m                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m16[0m[39m:==================================================================== *[0m[35m/[0m          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m17[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m18[0m[39m:package org.apache.poi.xssf.usermodel;[0m                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m19[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m20[0m[39m:import java.util.List;[0m                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode[0m[39m>[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode_snippets[0m[39m>[0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Fix Strategy[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<fix_strategy>[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[39m. Overview  [0m                                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   We need to fix three compilation errors introduced by the last patch while [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mpreserving its security and ZIP‐validation logic, and also silence strict [0m          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mdeprecation‐as‐error failures in BaseXSSFEvaluationWorkbook. Specifically:  [0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   a. Remove calls to the missing `[0m[1;35mgetByteCount[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` on Commons-IO’s [0m                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`BoundedInputStream` [0m[1;39m([0m[39mthe on-classpath version lacks that method[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.  [0m                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   b. Split out illegal multi-catch blocks combining `InvalidZipException` [0m[1;39m([0m[39ma [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39msubclass[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m with `IOException`.  [0m                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   c. Suppress deprecation-as-error in `BaseXSSFEvaluationWorkbook` so existing [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39muses of `[0m[1;35mXSSFWorkbook.getNameAt[0m[1;39m([0m[33m...[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` and `[0m[1;35mgetNameIndex[0m[1;39m([0m[33m...[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` compile under [0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`-Werror` without changing logic.  [0m                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m. Patch ZipPackage.java – InputStream constructor  [0m                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   a. Keep the magic‐header check and creation of a bounded temp file exactly as [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mbefore.  [0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   b. In the try-with-resources, wrap the [0m[1;39m([0m[39mbuffered & marked[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m input stream in `new [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;35mBoundedInputStream[0m[1;39m([0m[39mbin, maxBytes[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` to cap reads at `maxBytes`. Copy it into the [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mtemp file.  [0m                                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   c. **After** the try-with-resources [0m[1;39m([0m[39monce all streams are closed[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, inspect the [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mfilesystem size of the temp file:  [0m                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        if [0m[1;39m([0m[1;35mtmp.length[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m >= maxBytes[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m[39m  [0m                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m          throw new [0m[1;35mIOException[0m[1;39m([0m[39m…“Input ZIP exceeds maximum allowed size…”[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;  [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        [0m[1;39m}[0m[39m  [0m                                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      This preserves the size‐limit enforcement without calling the missing [0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`[0m[1;35mgetByteCount[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`.  [0m                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   d. Continue to open the temp file via `[0m[1;35mZipHelper.openZipFile[0m[1;39m([0m[39mtmp[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`.  [0m            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3[0m[39m. Patch ZipPackage.java – File constructor  [0m                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   Locate the block roughly around lines [0m[1;36m274[0m[39m–[0m[1;36m286[0m[39m:  [0m                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     try [0m[1;39m{[0m[39m  [0m                                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       ZipFile zipFile = [0m[1;35mZipHelper.openZipFile[0m[1;39m([0m[39mfile[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;  [0m                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       ze = new [0m[1;35mZipFileZipEntrySource[0m[1;39m([0m[39mzipFile[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;  [0m                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     [0m[1;39m}[0m[39m catch [0m[1;39m([0m[39mInvalidZipException | IOException e[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m[39m … [0m[1;39m}[0m[39m  [0m                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   Replace it with two sequential catches:  [0m                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     [0m[1;39m}[0m[39m catch [0m[1;39m([0m[39mInvalidZipException e[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m[39m  [0m                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       throw new [0m[1;35mInvalidOperationException[0m[1;39m([0m[32m"Can't open the specified file: '"[0m[39m + [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mfile + [0m[32m"'"[0m[39m, e[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;  [0m                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     [0m[1;39m}[0m[39m catch [0m[1;39m([0m[39mIOException e[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m[39m  [0m                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       if [0m[1;39m([0m[39maccess == PackageAccess.WRITE[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m[39m  [0m                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         throw new [0m[1;35mInvalidOperationException[0m[1;39m([0m[32m"Can't open the specified file: '"[0m[39m + [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mfile + [0m[32m"'"[0m[39m, e[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;  [0m                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       [0m[1;39m}[0m[39m  [0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       [0m[1;35mLOG.atWarn[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[1;35m.log[0m[1;39m([0m[32m"Error in zip file [0m[32m{[0m[32m}[0m[32m - falling back to stream processing"[0m[39m,[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mfile[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;  [0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       ze = [0m[1;35mopenZipEntrySourceStream[0m[1;39m([0m[39mfile[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;  [0m                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     [0m[1;39m}[0m[39m  [0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m4[0m[39m. Suppress deprecation errors in BaseXSSFEvaluationWorkbook.java  [0m                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   At the top of the class [0m[1;39m([0m[39mimmediately above `public class [0m                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mBaseXSSFEvaluationWorkbook`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, add:  [0m                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     @[0m[1;35mSuppressWarnings[0m[1;39m([0m[32m"deprecation"[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m  [0m                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   This silences deprecation warnings that are escalated to errors under the [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mproject’s strict compiler flags, without altering any existing API calls or logic. [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m5[0m[39m. Justification & Preservation of Existing Logic  [0m                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - The magic‐header test and bounded copy into a temp file are unchanged, so we [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mstill fast-fail non-ZIP data and cap overall ZIP size.  [0m                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Checking `[0m[1;35mtmp.length[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` enforces the same limit as the original [0m               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`[0m[1;35mgetByteCount[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` check.  [0m                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Splitting the multi-catch preserves the two distinct error-handling paths [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mexactly as before.  [0m                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Suppressing deprecation in `BaseXSSFEvaluationWorkbook` leaves [0m                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mformula-evaluation logic untouched, avoiding invasive API migrations.  [0m             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m6[0m[39m. Side Effects & Mitigations  [0m                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - The size check now uses file size, which on some platforms may differ by a few[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mbytes due to file metadata; but since we compare `>= maxBytes`, any truncated copy [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m([0m[39mcaused by hitting the BoundedInputStream limit[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m will trigger as intended.  [0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - If a future update upgrades Commons-IO to a version with `[0m[1;35mgetByteCount[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`, [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mthis workaround will still compile and continue to work, so it’s [0m                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mforward-compatible.  [0m                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - We avoid touching harness or test code; all existing tests and fuzzer [0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mentrypoints remain valid.  [0m                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m7[0m[39m. Verification  [0m                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   After patching, re-run `mvn clean install` [0m[1;39m([0m[39mor the project’s Gradle build[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mverifying:  [0m                                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - `ZipPackage` compiles without errors.  [0m                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - `poi-ooxml` module builds successfully.  [0m                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - No deprecation failures in `BaseXSSFEvaluationWorkbook`.  [0m                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - A quick smoke test with a valid ZIP and a non-ZIP input confirms the same [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mexception paths and size-limit enforcement as originally intended.  [0m                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mfix_strategy[0m[1m>[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         ===Evaluation [33mEnd[0m===                                                                [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Summary[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mThe initial issue surfaced as a fuzzer timeout [0m[1;39m([0m[39m`ERROR: libFuzzer: timeout`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m while [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mexercising the Apache POI OOXML codebase. In response, a patch was applied to the [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`ZipPackage` constructor to [0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m1[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m fast-fail on non-ZIP inputs by checking the PK [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mheader, [0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m2[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m copy the incoming stream into a bounded temporary file [0m[1;39m([0m[39musing [0m          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`BoundedInputStream` and `ZipSecureFile` limits[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, and [0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m3[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m switch from [0m              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`ZipInputStreamZipEntrySource` to `ZipFileZipEntrySource`. A minor annotation [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mchange [0m[1;39m([0m[39m`@[0m[1;35mSuppressWarnings[0m[1;39m([0m[32m"deprecation"[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m was also added to [0m                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`BaseXSSFEvaluationWorkbook`. After applying these changes, the fuzzer still [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mreports the same timeout error.[0m                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Description[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode_snippets[0m[39m>[0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Fix Strategy[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<fix_strategy>[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[39m. Ensure the InputStream‐based constructor always uses the fast, random‐access [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mpath  [0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   a. Remove any residual calls to ZipHelper.openZipStream followed by [0m             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mZipInputStreamZipEntrySource.  [0m                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   b. Retain the “PK” magic‐header check, BoundedInputStream copy [0m[1;39m([0m[39mup to maxBytes[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m,[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mand TempFile write logic introduced in the last patch.  [0m                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   c. After writing the bounded temp file, open it with [0m[1;35mZipHelper.openZipFile[0m[1;39m([0m[39mtmp[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mand wrap in ZipFileZipEntrySource—never fall back to streaming.  [0m                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   d. Honor the closeStream flag on the original InputStream: if [0m[33mcloseStream[0m[39m==true,[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mclose the wrapped BufferedInputStream once the temp file copy is complete.  [0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m. Disable the slow streaming fallback in the File‐based constructor  [0m              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   a. In [0m[1;35mZipPackage[0m[1;39m([0m[39mFile, …[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, replace the [0m[1;35mcatch[0m[1;39m([0m[39mIOException[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m block that logs a [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mwarning and calls [0m[1;35mopenZipEntrySourceStream[0m[1;39m([0m[39mfile[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m with a direct rethrow of [0m          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mInvalidOperationException.  [0m                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   b. This prevents any use of ZipInputStreamZipEntrySource [0m[1;39m([0m[39mwhich eagerly [0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mdecompresses every entry[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m in the file path.  [0m                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   c. Malformed or unreadable ZIP files will now fail fast rather than enter an [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39munbounded, blocking decompression loop.  [0m                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3[0m[39m. Eliminate openZipEntrySourceStream entirely [0m[1;39m([0m[39mor deprecate its use[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m  [0m             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   a. Remove or mark private the [0m[1;35mopenZipEntrySourceStream[0m[1;39m([0m[39mFile[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m helper; it [0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcurrently chains back into ZipHelper.openZipStream → ZipInputStreamZipEntrySource [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mand is the hotspot for timeouts.  [0m                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   b. If backward compatibility requires a “stream” fallback, implement a [0m          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mlightweight streaming metadata‐only reader that does not decompress entry contents,[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mbut preferably throw an exception and surface invalid ZIPs immediately.[0m             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m4[0m[39m. Preserve existing limits and safety checks  [0m                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   a. Keep the BoundedInputStream limit [0m[1;39m([0m[39mmaxEntrySize × maxFileCount[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m to guard [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39magainst zip bombs during the copy phase.  [0m                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   b. Continue to throw IOException if the temp file reaches maxBytes.  [0m            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   c. Maintain proper temp file cleanup [0m[1;39m([0m[39mdeleteOnExit[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m and resource closure.  [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m5[0m[39m. Validation and testing  [0m                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   a. Add unit tests for:  [0m                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      - Non‐ZIP inputs [0m[1;39m([0m[39mshould throw NotOfficeXmlFileException quickly[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.  [0m          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      - Overly large inputs [0m[1;39m([0m[39m>maxBytes[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m([0m[39mshould throw the size‐limit IOException[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m. [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      - Malformed or truncated central directories via File path [0m[1;39m([0m[39mshould throw [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mInvalidOperationException, no streaming fallback[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.  [0m                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   b. Rerun the libFuzzer harness to confirm no timeouts occur.  [0m                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mJustification  [0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- The root cause of the fuzzer timeouts is the eager, unbounded decompression in [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mZipInputStreamZipEntrySource—especially when triggered by the fallback path. By [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mforcing both InputStream and File constructors to only use ZipFileZipEntrySource [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m([0m[39mcentral directory parsing, no entry decompression[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, we eliminate the blocking [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mhotspot.  [0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Removing the streaming fallback sacrifices “best‐effort” recovery of malformed [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mzips but is acceptable given the fuzzer context and the fact that legitimate OOXML [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mfiles will use the fast central‐directory path.  [0m                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- All other logic [0m[1;39m([0m[39msignature checks, size bounds, resource closures[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m remains [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39munchanged, ensuring no regression in security or functional behavior.  [0m             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- This strategy does not touch the harness, fuzzing flags, or any external [0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mlibraries. It only modifies ZipPackage constructors to avoid the slow code path.[0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mfix_strategy[0m[1m>[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         ===Evaluation [33mEnd[0m===                                                                [2m                [0m
